com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.grabber

Interface Grabber<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Elements type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGrabber, ArrayGrabber, ListGrabber, StringCharGrabber

    public interface Grabber<T>
    Element grab utility. This class grabs elements and put them into a grab blacklist. Elements in the blacklist cannot be grabbed again, some methods will not returns elements in the blacklist. Grab methods can only grab whitelisted elements (Whitelisted elements are all elements that are not in the blacklist). Methods marked as element consumer are methods that adds consumed elements to the blacklist.
